      "raw_text": "DENVER, March 31.---A confer\nence between the Gould railroad\nofficials and union men will better\nmine the question of a general\nstrike on the road or renewal of a\nclosed shop contract. The issue is\nbased on the closed shop. Boiler\nmakers and blacksmiths have voted\nto strike if the contracts are not\nrenewed"
    }
